WEBVTT

1
00:00:22.278 --> 00:00:23.877
Where am I?

2
00:00:24.177 --> 00:00:25.217
What happened?

3
00:00:25.677 --> 00:00:27.147
I'm sure I went through that manhole.

4
00:00:30.557 --> 00:00:31.587
Soo Jin!

5
00:00:37.727 --> 00:00:38.727
Soo Jin!

6
00:00:53.338 --> 00:00:55.647
Soo Jin, are you all right?

7
00:00:57.418 --> 00:00:58.547
Who's that darned...

8
00:00:58.547 --> 00:00:59.948
Pil, let's go. We have to go.

9
00:00:59.948 --> 00:01:01.287
- Why? - That's Jae Hyun's car.

10
00:01:01.287 --> 00:01:02.388
- Really? - Hurry.

11
00:01:48.927 --> 00:01:50.938
(Episode 15)

12
00:02:05.048 --> 00:02:06.218
Soo Jin, are you okay?

13
00:02:07.387 --> 00:02:08.848
What...

14
00:02:09.947 --> 00:02:12.058
What happened?

15
00:02:12.257 --> 00:02:13.417
You must've been shocked.

16
00:02:14.158 --> 00:02:15.558
Did you get hurt?

17
00:02:16.088 --> 00:02:17.197
Pil.

18
00:02:18.357 --> 00:02:20.368
I remember...

19
00:02:21.398 --> 00:02:22.667
what just happened.

20
00:02:26.368 --> 00:02:30.137
Last time I saved you,

21
00:02:31.878 --> 00:02:34.808
but this time you saved me.

22
00:02:45.688 --> 00:02:47.957
- Soo Jin. - Yes?

23
00:02:50.457 --> 00:02:52.028
How do you remember that?

24
00:02:53.327 --> 00:02:56.297
I don't know. I just remember everything.

25
00:02:57.237 --> 00:02:59.737
The same situation happened again.

26
00:03:01.207 --> 00:03:02.968
I fell from the rooftop...

27
00:03:02.968 --> 00:03:04.908
trying to escape from Jae Hyun.

28
00:03:05.408 --> 00:03:07.408
You grabbed me last time.

29
00:03:08.648 --> 00:03:11.218
How did I come back here?

30
00:03:13.748 --> 00:03:15.947
What's going on, Pil?

31
00:03:19.158 --> 00:03:20.558
I believe...

32
00:03:24.297 --> 00:03:26.197
we rode the manhole together this time.

33
00:03:27.868 --> 00:03:28.928
What?

34
00:03:29.667 --> 00:03:31.767
Ride the manhole?

35
00:04:21.087 --> 00:04:22.147
Why on earth...

36
00:04:23.757 --> 00:04:26.118
did you meet Pil?

37
00:04:28.387 --> 00:04:29.387
Were you...

38
00:04:30.527 --> 00:04:32.197
trying to report me?

39
00:04:34.998 --> 00:04:36.428
No way.

40
00:04:38.738 --> 00:04:40.837
You'd never do that.

41
00:04:46.378 --> 00:04:48.147
(Jin Sook)

42
00:04:55.688 --> 00:04:56.748
Hi, Jin Sook.

43
00:04:56.887 --> 00:04:57.988
Jae Hyun?

44
00:04:58.517 --> 00:04:59.988
Where's Soo Jin?

45
00:04:59.988 --> 00:05:02.858
I think she went out for a walk.

46
00:05:03.257 --> 00:05:04.858
I see.

47
00:05:05.327 --> 00:05:06.897
Okay. Please tell her...

48
00:05:06.897 --> 00:05:09.767
to call me when she gets back.

49
00:05:11.637 --> 00:05:12.697
Okay.

50
00:05:18.608 --> 00:05:20.137
Jin Sook.

51
00:05:21.108 --> 00:05:23.108
What? What's wrong? Why the long face?

52
00:05:23.108 --> 00:05:25.077
Soo Jin came by.

53
00:05:25.077 --> 00:05:26.947
She looked really upset.

54
00:05:27.087 --> 00:05:28.517
I called her,

55
00:05:28.517 --> 00:05:29.847
but Jae Hyun answered.

56
00:05:29.947 --> 00:05:32.217
Really? Is something wrong?

57
00:05:32.587 --> 00:05:33.757
I'm not sure.

58
00:05:34.087 --> 00:05:36.228
Do you think she had a fight with Jae Hyun?

59
00:05:37.128 --> 00:05:38.197
I'm worried.

60
00:05:39.027 --> 00:05:41.097
Lovers' quarrels never lasts long, you know.

61
00:05:41.097 --> 00:05:42.168
They'll make up soon.

62
00:05:42.168 --> 00:05:43.267
Right?

63
00:05:43.697 --> 00:05:45.238
I'm sure it's nothing.

64
00:05:45.238 --> 00:05:46.368
By the way,

65
00:05:46.368 --> 00:05:48.438
I saw Pil by the manhole.

66
00:05:48.438 --> 00:05:49.907
Again? Why?

67
00:05:49.967 --> 00:05:52.077
Is he trying to dig it up again?

68
00:05:52.438 --> 00:05:54.548
He's having a tough time getting over Soo Jin.

69
00:05:55.378 --> 00:05:58.748
It's hard for him to see her married to someone.

70
00:05:58.847 --> 00:06:01.347
He wants to travel back in time.

71
00:06:02.017 --> 00:06:03.387
That's ridiculous.

72
00:06:03.788 --> 00:06:05.517
He must be crazy.

73
00:06:05.517 --> 00:06:06.788
He's insane.

74
00:06:07.228 --> 00:06:08.327
I know.

75
00:06:08.488 --> 00:06:10.697
I think Pil will make a huge trouble soon.

76
00:06:11.097 --> 00:06:12.657
When will he grow up?

77
00:06:21.707 --> 00:06:22.767
Drink this.

78
00:06:23.108 --> 00:06:24.238
Thanks.

79
00:06:27.407 --> 00:06:28.407
Pil.

80
00:06:30.418 --> 00:06:31.548
So you're saying...

81
00:06:32.418 --> 00:06:35.717
that we traveled time through the manhole?

82
00:06:36.548 --> 00:06:37.558
Yes.

83
00:06:38.318 --> 00:06:40.527
Normally, I traveled time alone,

84
00:06:42.157 --> 00:06:43.897
but for some reason,

85
00:06:44.097 --> 00:06:45.957
we rode the manhole together this time.

86
00:06:49.628 --> 00:06:51.967
Even though I experienced it, it's hard to believe.

87
00:06:54.137 --> 00:06:56.007
How can this happen?

88
00:06:56.407 --> 00:06:58.438
I know how confused you are...

89
00:06:59.108 --> 00:07:00.777
right now.

90
00:07:02.207 --> 00:07:04.777
I was confused like you at first.

91
00:07:08.587 --> 00:07:10.017
Anyway...

92
00:07:10.688 --> 00:07:12.918
Jae Hyun was the hit-and-run driver.

93
00:07:13.657 --> 00:07:15.257
It's shocking.

94
00:07:15.988 --> 00:07:17.558
How can he stay by your side...

95
00:07:17.558 --> 00:07:19.697
when he's the one who hit you?

96
00:07:24.197 --> 00:07:25.967
You were right, Pil.

97
00:07:27.808 --> 00:07:28.907
About what?

98
00:07:29.907 --> 00:07:31.837
The assailant for the random attacks...

99
00:07:36.147 --> 00:07:37.847
was Jae Hyun.

100
00:07:41.447 --> 00:07:42.918
How did you find out?

101
00:07:46.587 --> 00:07:48.228
I found...

102
00:07:49.257 --> 00:07:53.358
the mask, cap, and clothes I saw on the news...

103
00:07:53.798 --> 00:07:56.967
in Jae Hyun's car trunk.

104
00:08:00.738 --> 00:08:02.137
I knew then...

105
00:08:04.108 --> 00:08:06.077
that he was the assailant.

106
00:08:10.007 --> 00:08:12.118
That's why I called you.

107
00:08:13.378 --> 00:08:15.347
I figured I needed your help.

108
00:08:19.788 --> 00:08:21.087
What should we do now?

109
00:08:22.928 --> 00:08:25.858
Should we report Jae Hyun to the police?

110
00:08:26.428 --> 00:08:27.467
No.

111
00:08:28.498 --> 00:08:31.637
I want to wrap my head around it first.

112
00:08:32.597 --> 00:08:34.367
I'm just too overwhelmed.

113
00:08:35.408 --> 00:08:37.178
I can't make any decisions right now.

114
00:08:40.847 --> 00:08:41.908
Okay.

115
00:08:43.278 --> 00:08:45.717
Let's think about what we're going to do.

116
00:08:46.178 --> 00:08:47.188
Okay.

117
00:08:55.188 --> 00:08:57.197
I'll take that. Be careful.

118
00:09:16.008 --> 00:09:18.117
(Yangyang 65km, Gangneung 12km)

119
00:09:25.457 --> 00:09:26.518
Uncle!

120
00:09:28.158 --> 00:09:29.888
- Uncle! - Who is it?

121
00:09:31.258 --> 00:09:33.058
Who the heck is it?

122
00:09:33.727 --> 00:09:35.668
What? Pil?

123
00:09:35.668 --> 00:09:37.997
- It's me, Uncle. - Hey.

124
00:09:37.997 --> 00:09:40.668
Why are you here this late?

125
00:09:42.068 --> 00:09:43.068
- What? - Hi.

126
00:09:43.138 --> 00:09:45.408
Wait. I know you.

127
00:09:45.408 --> 00:09:48.678
You're Pil's friend...

128
00:09:49.077 --> 00:09:50.818
Hello. You remember.

129
00:09:50.818 --> 00:09:52.918
Of course, I do.

130
00:09:52.918 --> 00:09:55.918
Pil used to follow you around...

131
00:09:55.918 --> 00:09:57.087
all the time.

132
00:09:57.087 --> 00:09:59.957
You don't have to bring that up.

133
00:09:59.957 --> 00:10:00.957
That was a long time ago.

134
00:10:00.957 --> 00:10:04.997
By the way, why are you here so late?

135
00:10:04.997 --> 00:10:07.727
- Well... - I see.

136
00:10:08.127 --> 00:10:11.197
I guess you guys are finally going out.

137
00:10:13.337 --> 00:10:15.967
Are you on a night trip to see the beach?

138
00:10:16.038 --> 00:10:17.938
No, it's not like that.

139
00:10:17.938 --> 00:10:20.408
We were in the area for some other business.

140
00:10:21.207 --> 00:10:23.548
Uncle. Can you let us sleep over?

141
00:10:23.548 --> 00:10:24.877
What? Sleep over?

142
00:10:24.877 --> 00:10:26.847
Of course. Come in.

143
00:10:26.847 --> 00:10:29.347
Uncle, do you have a first aid kit?

144
00:10:29.347 --> 00:10:30.558
First aid kit?

145
00:10:31.087 --> 00:10:33.158
Why? Did someone get hurt?

146
00:10:40.367 --> 00:10:41.367
Does it hurt a lot?

147
00:10:42.127 --> 00:10:43.898
Should we go to the hospital?

148
00:10:45.597 --> 00:10:47.638
I think it's more serious than we think.

149
00:10:47.638 --> 00:10:49.508
It's not that serious.

150
00:10:50.337 --> 00:10:51.638
I can do it.

151
00:10:51.638 --> 00:10:53.577
Stay still. I'll do it.

152
00:10:54.607 --> 00:10:55.607
Wait.

153
00:10:59.577 --> 00:11:01.347
Look at this.

154
00:11:01.347 --> 00:11:02.447
It'll leave a scar.

155
00:11:04.888 --> 00:11:06.558
If it hurts too much, let me know.

156
00:11:06.558 --> 00:11:08.758
I'll take you to the hospital, okay?

157
00:11:14.668 --> 00:11:15.668
Hold on.

158
00:11:17.138 --> 00:11:19.337
You got hurt too.

159
00:11:19.568 --> 00:11:21.068
It's pretty bad.

160
00:11:21.068 --> 00:11:22.467
Didn't you know?

161
00:11:23.568 --> 00:11:25.077
Goodness.

162
00:11:31.747 --> 00:11:33.217
Oh, no.

163
00:11:38.288 --> 00:11:39.418
You must've gotten this...

164
00:11:39.418 --> 00:11:41.227
when you rolled over to save me a while ago.

165
00:11:44.428 --> 00:11:45.428
I guess so.

166
00:11:45.597 --> 00:11:47.898
Take care of yourself before you...

167
00:11:47.898 --> 00:11:49.398
take care of me from now on.

168
00:11:50.997 --> 00:11:52.597
It's upsetting to see you...

169
00:11:53.068 --> 00:11:54.268
get hurt because of me.

170
00:11:58.077 --> 00:11:59.678
Gosh, it must hurt a lot.

171
00:12:14.388 --> 00:12:17.227
This much first-aid should be enough.

172
00:12:18.357 --> 00:12:20.097
Let's go to a hospital tomorrow...

173
00:12:20.298 --> 00:12:21.497
if it gets worse.

174
00:12:22.467 --> 00:12:23.467
Okay.

175
00:12:28.867 --> 00:12:29.867
By the way,

176
00:12:30.908 --> 00:12:33.308
shouldn't you call your parents?

177
00:12:33.308 --> 00:12:35.778
Oh, right. I should.

178
00:12:36.508 --> 00:12:37.518
My...

179
00:12:38.518 --> 00:12:39.518
What?

180
00:12:39.947 --> 00:12:41.048
Where's my cellphone?

181
00:12:42.217 --> 00:12:44.288
I think I dropped it somewhere.

182
00:12:44.617 --> 00:12:46.087
Let me use your cellphone.

183
00:12:46.117 --> 00:12:47.127
Okay.

184
00:12:49.028 --> 00:12:50.058
Thanks.

185
00:12:54.367 --> 00:12:56.367
(My Precious)

186
00:13:12.847 --> 00:13:15.018
(Pil)

187
00:13:26.528 --> 00:13:27.597
Hello?

188
00:13:28.827 --> 00:13:30.068
Hello?

189
00:13:31.467 --> 00:13:33.268
Did you pick up this phone by any chance?

190
00:13:33.967 --> 00:13:35.308
Hello?

191
00:13:36.168 --> 00:13:37.237
Hello?

192
00:13:42.778 --> 00:13:43.778
What's wrong?

193
00:13:44.648 --> 00:13:45.648
I don't know.

194
00:13:46.278 --> 00:13:48.117
They listened without saying anything...

195
00:13:48.117 --> 00:13:49.117
and hung up.

196
00:13:51.518 --> 00:13:52.617
Kang Soo Jin.

197
00:13:54.327 --> 00:13:57.357
So are you really going to spend the night with him?

198
00:13:58.097 --> 00:14:00.227
Hey. Who are you?

199
00:14:00.497 --> 00:14:02.398
You can't set a fire here.

200
00:14:02.398 --> 00:14:05.038
What if it spreads to the construction materials?

201
00:14:05.138 --> 00:14:06.697
Who are you?

202
00:14:06.967 --> 00:14:08.607
Goodness.

203
00:14:26.117 --> 00:14:27.127
Here.

204
00:14:28.788 --> 00:14:31.997
Fortunately, my uncle washed these blankets.

205
00:14:33.227 --> 00:14:35.627
He always keeps things clean and neat.

206
00:14:36.227 --> 00:14:38.798
Pil, you need to go get some sleep too.

207
00:14:38.798 --> 00:14:40.138
I'll do the rest.

208
00:14:40.138 --> 00:14:41.737
All right.

209
00:14:42.967 --> 00:14:44.308
- Good night. - Good night.

210
00:14:45.837 --> 00:14:48.207
What? What's going on?

211
00:14:49.048 --> 00:14:50.418
Did the power go off?

212
00:15:00.658 --> 00:15:03.758
- I'll go see... - Wait, don't go.

213
00:15:03.758 --> 00:15:06.197
Pil, don't go. I'm scared.

214
00:15:06.197 --> 00:15:08.568
- Don't go. - But I still need to...

215
00:15:08.568 --> 00:15:12.097
Hold on. Let me go with you then. I'm scared.

216
00:15:12.097 --> 00:15:13.837
- Okay. Let's go together. - Pil.

217
00:15:20.577 --> 00:15:21.607
It's on again.

218
00:15:23.048 --> 00:15:24.678
- You're right. - It went on.

219
00:15:24.678 --> 00:15:25.678
My gosh.

220
00:15:25.678 --> 00:15:26.947
Thank goodness.

221
00:15:27.788 --> 00:15:29.418
Get some rest now.

222
00:15:29.418 --> 00:15:30.418
Well...

223
00:15:30.518 --> 00:15:34.127
Where will you sleep by the way?

224
00:15:34.127 --> 00:15:36.727
I'll sleep somewhere over there.

225
00:15:36.727 --> 00:15:38.857
Okay, goodnight.

226
00:15:38.957 --> 00:15:40.127
- Bye. - Bye.

227
00:15:42.268 --> 00:15:44.497
Goodness.

228
00:15:47.638 --> 00:15:48.737
Are you okay?

229
00:16:04.758 --> 00:16:05.818
Soo Jin.

230
00:16:06.188 --> 00:16:07.188
What?

231
00:16:09.957 --> 00:16:10.997
Should we just...

232
00:16:12.097 --> 00:16:13.898
stay here instead of going back to Seoul?

233
00:16:17.197 --> 00:16:18.268
What are you...

234
00:16:18.898 --> 00:16:20.638
talking about all of a sudden?

235
00:16:21.768 --> 00:16:22.768
Well...

236
00:16:23.508 --> 00:16:24.508
It's just...

237
00:16:24.908 --> 00:16:26.908
that I don't want to be apart from you.

238
00:16:40.087 --> 00:16:43.798
Tell me if you need anything else.

239
00:16:44.857 --> 00:16:46.898
I'll go buy some stuff at the convenience store.

240
00:16:47.227 --> 00:16:48.367
Rest here.

241
00:16:48.967 --> 00:16:50.127
Okay.

242
00:17:09.687 --> 00:17:12.357
Why did you say you didn't want to go back to Seoul?

243
00:17:15.058 --> 00:17:16.458
Wake up, Pil.

244
00:17:31.482 --> 00:17:34.714
<font color="#80ffff">[VIU Ver] Episode 15 Manhole "Turn Yourself In"</font>
<font color="#ff80ff">-= Ruo Xi =-</font>

245
00:17:47.728 --> 00:17:48.788
Soo Jin.

246
00:20:23.478 --> 00:20:24.478
Soo Jin.

247
00:20:31.758 --> 00:20:32.758
Soo Jin.

248
00:20:51.208 --> 00:20:52.208
Pil.

249
00:20:53.708 --> 00:20:57.077
When you warned me that Jae Hyun was dangerous,

250
00:20:57.077 --> 00:20:58.617
why didn't I trust you?

251
00:21:00.048 --> 00:21:02.248
If I had listened to you at least once,

252
00:21:03.018 --> 00:21:05.258
things wouldn't have ended up this way.

253
00:21:07.127 --> 00:21:09.127
You didn't have a choice.

254
00:21:10.228 --> 00:21:12.157
He's the guy you chose.

255
00:21:13.127 --> 00:21:14.728
I'm sure you wanted to trust him.

256
00:21:18.468 --> 00:21:20.167
As I traveled through time,

257
00:21:20.867 --> 00:21:24.208
I came to realize that he wasn't a good man.

258
00:21:25.177 --> 00:21:26.308
But...

259
00:21:27.278 --> 00:21:29.008
no matter how the situation turns out,

260
00:21:30.077 --> 00:21:32.448
you just got closer and closer to him.

261
00:21:33.347 --> 00:21:35.988
I didn't know how I could bring this up.

262
00:21:39.058 --> 00:21:40.587
In order to convince you that I'm right,

263
00:21:41.427 --> 00:21:44.357
I knew I had to tell you that I have been...

264
00:21:44.357 --> 00:21:45.528
traveling through time.

265
00:21:47.427 --> 00:21:49.468
But there was no way you would believe that.

266
00:21:51.068 --> 00:21:52.768
That was the most frustrating.

267
00:21:56.367 --> 00:21:57.677
I get it now.

268
00:22:00.847 --> 00:22:02.508
It must've been...

269
00:22:03.048 --> 00:22:05.048
really frustrating and difficult for you.

270
00:22:08.347 --> 00:22:09.448
Pil.

271
00:22:10.248 --> 00:22:11.788
What on earth happened...

272
00:22:12.218 --> 00:22:14.187
as you traveled through time?

273
00:22:18.127 --> 00:22:19.597
A lot of things happened.

274
00:22:20.198 --> 00:22:21.927
You just don't know what they are.

275
00:22:24.397 --> 00:22:26.437
Whenever you were in danger,

276
00:22:26.937 --> 00:22:28.367
I saved you.

277
00:22:29.068 --> 00:22:31.177
Once I was unconscious...

278
00:22:31.177 --> 00:22:33.907
and spoke with you as a spirit.

279
00:22:34.708 --> 00:22:36.147
Come on.

280
00:22:40.117 --> 00:22:41.818
You might not remember,

281
00:22:41.917 --> 00:22:44.117
but you even asked me to marry you.

282
00:22:44.318 --> 00:22:46.788
Did I? Really?

283
00:22:46.788 --> 00:22:47.857
Yes.

284
00:22:49.627 --> 00:22:52.597
But after I got into the manhole again,

285
00:22:52.597 --> 00:22:54.867
everything that happened disappeared,

286
