He's dangerous. You might get hurt.

565
00:39:35.598 --> 00:39:37.738
Deciding not to see you...

566
00:39:39.598 --> 00:39:41.707
has nothing to do with Jae Hyun.

567
00:39:43.607 --> 00:39:45.138
It's just what I decided.

568
00:39:51.618 --> 00:39:52.618
Pil.

569
00:39:54.348 --> 00:39:56.787
I want you to be happy.

570
00:40:00.787 --> 00:40:03.357
I don't know if you'll time travel again...

571
00:40:05.357 --> 00:40:08.468
or if you'll stay here.

572
00:40:09.868 --> 00:40:11.068
But from now on,

573
00:40:12.337 --> 00:40:14.267
regardless of what happens,

574
00:40:16.937 --> 00:40:18.707
don't choose me.

575
00:40:24.377 --> 00:40:25.917
I don't want...

576
00:40:27.618 --> 00:40:29.988
you to suffer because of me.

577
00:40:36.187 --> 00:40:37.557
I'll get going first.

578
00:40:39.028 --> 00:40:40.057
Take your time.

579
00:42:22.528 --> 00:42:24.337
Jae Hyun.

580
00:42:25.767 --> 00:42:26.937
Soo Jin.

581
00:42:41.848 --> 00:42:42.888
Soo Jin.

582
00:42:45.357 --> 00:42:46.658
Let's talk.

583
00:42:48.328 --> 00:42:51.198
Please hear me out.

584
00:42:54.568 --> 00:42:55.598
Please.

585
00:43:09.908 --> 00:43:11.548
How did you know I'm here?

586
00:43:11.977 --> 00:43:13.718
The cellphone which you dropped.

587
00:43:14.687 --> 00:43:16.187
I kept it all along.

588
00:43:18.087 --> 00:43:20.118
I read your billing history and came here.

589
00:43:25.098 --> 00:43:26.158
Soo Jin.

590
00:43:26.897 --> 00:43:28.897
I know you're very disappointed in me.

591
00:43:30.368 --> 00:43:32.098
You must've been so surprised and scared...

592
00:43:33.707 --> 00:43:35.937
when you found out what I did.

593
00:43:39.778 --> 00:43:41.008
I...

594
00:43:42.747 --> 00:43:43.848
can't forgive myself.

595
00:43:48.118 --> 00:43:50.988
When I was with Pil last night,

596
00:43:53.618 --> 00:43:54.658
did you...

597
00:43:55.627 --> 00:43:57.227
try to hit us with your car on purpose?

598
00:43:59.357 --> 00:44:01.127
When I saw you with Pil,

599
00:44:03.267 --> 00:44:04.468
I got mad.

600
00:44:06.198 --> 00:44:08.408
I did it without realizing what I was doing.

601
00:44:10.037 --> 00:44:11.607
Do you think that justifies it?

602
00:44:12.178 --> 00:44:13.207
So...

603
00:44:16.578 --> 00:44:18.477
Is that why you...

604
00:44:19.578 --> 00:44:20.718
randomly attack people?

605
00:44:21.587 --> 00:44:22.848
I don't know.

606
00:44:23.488 --> 00:44:24.587
I can't...

607
00:44:24.787 --> 00:44:26.818
control myself when I get mad.

608
00:44:27.727 --> 00:44:29.258
Even though I regret it,

609
00:44:30.258 --> 00:44:32.528
I can't control it. It drives me crazy.

610
00:44:36.298 --> 00:44:39.798
I still can't believe that you did such a thing.

611
00:44:42.908 --> 00:44:45.238
You were a nice person.

612
00:44:46.537 --> 00:44:48.278
But why did you do it?

613
00:44:51.118 --> 00:44:52.178
Never mind.

614
00:44:53.917 --> 00:44:55.787
Whatever excuse you give me,

615
00:44:56.548 --> 00:44:58.187
your deeds cannot...

616
00:44:58.658 --> 00:45:00.287
be overlooked.

617
00:45:04.428 --> 00:45:05.457
Jae Hyun.

618
00:45:08.568 --> 00:45:09.627
Turn yourself in.

619
00:45:11.497 --> 00:45:14.138
Pay for what you've done,

620
00:45:15.408 --> 00:45:16.738
and receive treatment.

621
00:45:19.138 --> 00:45:20.178
Then...

622
00:45:22.377 --> 00:45:24.147
you might get better.

623
00:45:30.287 --> 00:45:31.388
Okay.

624
00:45:32.787 --> 00:45:33.828
I'll turn myself in.

625
00:45:37.928 --> 00:45:39.298
Soo Jin,

626
00:45:41.198 --> 00:45:42.627
will you go with me?

627
00:45:53.238 --> 00:45:58.118
The person I loved

628
00:46:11.928 --> 00:46:13.057
Pil.

629
00:46:13.357 --> 00:46:14.828
Hi, Uncle. Where are you going?

630
00:46:14.828 --> 00:46:17.897
I'm going for grocery shopping.

631
00:46:18.298 --> 00:46:21.207
I saw Soo Jin with someone just now.

632
00:46:22.068 --> 00:46:23.508
- Someone? - Yes.

633
00:46:23.508 --> 00:46:25.908
He's about this tall.

634
00:46:26.037 --> 00:46:28.707
He looks manly and handsome.

635
00:46:29.607 --> 00:46:31.417
Who is he?

636
00:46:32.747 --> 00:46:35.448
Gosh, no.

637
00:46:35.448 --> 00:46:36.647
What?

638
00:47:31.008 --> 00:47:32.778
Park Jae Hyun is the culprit.

639
00:47:34.647 --> 00:47:36.247
Call the detective in charge.

640
00:47:36.508 --> 00:47:37.948
Tell him we've secured...

641
00:47:37.948 --> 00:47:39.517
the video footage of the assailant.

642
00:47:39.517 --> 00:47:40.818
Yes, sir.

643
00:47:44.258 --> 00:47:45.417
We should do something.

644
00:47:45.417 --> 00:47:47.857
Let's wait a little longer.

645
00:47:47.857 --> 00:47:49.388
Excuse me.

646
00:47:50.658 --> 00:47:52.758
We came in because the door was open.

647
00:47:52.857 --> 00:47:54.098
Excuse us.

648
00:47:54.328 --> 00:47:55.528
How may I help you?

649
00:47:55.528 --> 00:47:57.537
Is Ms. Kang Soo Jin here?

650
00:47:57.537 --> 00:47:58.897
She didn't answer her phone,

651
00:47:58.897 --> 00:48:00.228
and she wasn't at home,

652
00:48:00.253 --> 00:48:01.532
so we came here to see her.

653
00:48:02.508 --> 00:48:04.138
Why are you looking for my daughter?

654
00:48:04.377 --> 00:48:06.678
Did something happen to her?

655
00:48:07.508 --> 00:48:09.207
No, it's not that.

656
00:48:09.207 --> 00:48:11.778
Then why are you looking for her?

657
00:48:13.348 --> 00:48:14.787
Well...

658
00:48:15.448 --> 00:48:17.857
We want to ask her some things...

659
00:48:17.857 --> 00:48:19.917
regarding Mr. Park Jae Hyun.

660
00:48:19.917 --> 00:48:20.928
Park Jae Hyun?

661
00:48:21.828 --> 00:48:23.727
- Our son-in-law? - Yes,

662
00:48:24.028 --> 00:48:25.997
I'm sure you're aware of the random attacks...

663
00:48:25.997 --> 00:48:28.298
that have occurred in the neighborhood, right?

664
00:48:28.528 --> 00:48:29.698
- Yes. - Yes.

665
00:48:29.698 --> 00:48:32.497
What does it have to do with him though?

666
00:48:32.497 --> 00:48:34.037
Mr. Park...

667
00:48:34.468 --> 00:48:36.767
is the prime suspect of the case.

668
00:48:37.307 --> 00:48:39.238
- What? - What?

669
00:49:00.767 --> 00:49:01.798
Were you...

670
00:49:03.127 --> 00:49:05.098
with Pil last night?

671
00:49:05.468 --> 00:49:06.537
Yes.

672
00:49:08.937 --> 00:49:09.968
Did you...

673
00:49:10.707 --> 00:49:12.207
share a room with him?

674
00:49:14.948 --> 00:49:15.977
No.

675
00:49:16.678 --> 00:49:17.877
I can't do that.

676
00:49:17.977 --> 00:49:19.178
You're right.

677
00:49:19.448 --> 00:49:21.187
You would never do that.

678
00:49:35.198 --> 00:49:38.337
I thought we were going to Seoul.

679
00:49:39.537 --> 00:49:41.167
Why are you going this way?

680
00:49:42.807 --> 00:49:45.008
Let's drop by somewhere to get some fresh air.

681
00:49:47.977 --> 00:49:50.207
What are you talking about?

682
00:49:51.417 --> 00:49:53.247
You said you'd go turn yourself in.

683
00:49:54.218 --> 00:49:56.147
We couldn't even go on our trip to England.

684
00:49:56.147 --> 00:49:57.687
It'd be upsetting if we returned like this.

685
00:49:58.687 --> 00:50:00.357
We have enough time, so let's take it slow.

686
00:50:12.397 --> 00:50:13.468
Mr. Bong.

687
00:50:13.837 --> 00:50:14.868
Hello, Mr. Choi.

688
00:50:15.167 --> 00:50:17.278
Sorry, I'm a bit busy now.

689
00:50:17.278 --> 00:50:19.078
Are you with Soo Jin?

690
00:50:19.337 --> 00:50:20.377
What?

691
00:50:20.377 --> 00:50:22.548
If you are, come to Seoul with her quickly...

692
00:50:22.548 --> 00:50:23.977
so that she can testify.

693
00:50:25.917 --> 00:50:27.287
Like you said,

694
00:50:27.517 --> 00:50:29.118
Jae Hyun is the culprit.

695
00:50:29.318 --> 00:50:31.258
He turned his phone off...

696
00:50:31.258 --> 00:50:32.818
and is out of reach at the moment.

697
00:50:32.818 --> 00:50:33.928
I think he ran off.

698
00:50:33.928 --> 00:50:36.258
He's on the run in Gangneung...

699
00:50:36.258 --> 00:50:37.698
with Soo Jin now.

700
00:50:37.698 --> 00:50:39.658
- What? - I'm searching for them.

701
00:50:57.118 --> 00:50:59.917
Mr. Bong. What's going on?

702
00:51:13.457 --> 00:51:15.098
Why are you suddenly acting so weird?

703
00:51:51.537 --> 00:51:53.568
Hey, man. Learn how to drive.

704
00:52:06.618 --> 00:52:08.417
I think I lost Park Jae Hyun's vehicle.

705
00:52:09.048 --> 00:52:11.417
I'll search around the premise.

706
00:52:12.158 --> 00:52:13.158
Yes.

707
00:52:41.787 --> 00:52:42.948
You must be hungry.

708
00:52:43.118 --> 00:52:44.917
Give me a bit more time. I'll be done soon.

709
00:52:51.357 --> 00:52:52.357
Jae Hyun.

710
00:52:53.158 --> 00:52:54.698
Let's not do this,

711
00:52:54.897 --> 00:52:56.428
and go back to Seoul.

712
00:52:57.537 --> 00:53:00.068
You should go back and turn yourself in.

713
00:53:07.477 --> 00:53:09.408
It seems like you don't want to be here with me.

714
00:53:11.417 --> 00:53:12.448
What?

715
00:53:18.118 --> 00:53:20.017
It's been forever since we had a time like this.

716
00:53:20.428 --> 00:53:22.028
Let's forget about everything for now,

717
00:53:22.028 --> 00:53:23.187
and enjoy ourselves.

718
00:53:24.727 --> 00:53:25.798
Stay seated.

719
00:54:09.607 --> 00:54:10.977
(Your phone is loading.)

720
00:54:16.048 --> 00:54:17.048
(Pil)

721
00:54:23.318 --> 00:54:25.488
You must be hungry. Have this first.

722
00:54:25.587 --> 00:54:26.718
Sure, thanks.

723
00:54:31.127 --> 00:54:32.857
(Pil)

724
00:54:33.328 --> 00:54:34.397
Hello?

725
00:54:39.497 --> 00:54:40.638
Soo Jin.

726
00:54:40.968 --> 00:54:45.107
I finished cooking your favorite dish, steak.

727
00:55:04.158 --> 00:55:06.528
(Pil)

728
00:55:07.298 --> 00:55:09.098
Have some. I didn't have the right ingredients,

729
00:55:09.098 --> 00:55:10.468
so it might not be great.

730
00:55:10.468 --> 00:55:12.098
Sure, let's eat.

731
00:55:19.278 --> 00:55:21.278
How is it? Is it good?

732
00:55:21.278 --> 00:55:23.377
Yes, it's good.

733
00:55:24.647 --> 00:55:25.678
I had no idea...

734
00:55:26.618 --> 00:55:29.118
there was a place like this by the lake.

735
00:55:29.118 --> 00:55:30.457
Didn't I tell you?

736
00:55:31.118 --> 00:55:33.857
I think I said parents left me a summer house.

737
00:55:35.028 --> 00:55:36.388
I think you did.

738
00:55:37.698 --> 00:55:38.897
The lake we saw...

739
00:55:39.658 --> 00:55:42.028
on our way here was pretty splendid.

740
00:55:42.968 --> 00:55:44.298
What's it called?

741
00:55:47.267 --> 00:55:48.408
Haneul Lake.

742
00:55:50.037 --> 00:55:51.778
Oh, Haneul Lake.

743
00:55:53.747 --> 00:55:54.807
Isn't that a pretty name?

744
00:55:55.348 --> 00:55:57.318
It's prettier at dawn with the morning mist.

745
00:55:57.578 --> 00:55:58.718
It's really amazing.

746
00:55:59.848 --> 00:56:01.787
Okay, I'll make sure I catch that.

747
00:56:02.488 --> 00:56:03.587
Haneul Lake?

748
00:56:04.087 --> 00:56:05.457
Are you glad we came?

749
00:56:13.968 --> 00:56:14.968
Sure.

750
00:56:21.368 --> 00:56:23.468
(Pil)

751
00:57:16.957 --> 00:57:18.598
(49N4138)

752
00:57:24.568 --> 00:57:25.568
Thanks.

753
00:57:36.178 --> 00:57:37.848
- Soo Jin. - Yes?

754
00:57:38.848 --> 00:57:40.147
Should we leave Korea?

755
00:57:41.718 --> 00:57:42.917
What do you mean?

756
00:57:45.457 --> 00:57:47.627
If I turn myself in, I'll have to go to jail.

757
00:57:48.258 --> 00:57:50.287
Then you'll be too lonely by yourself.

758
00:57:55.198 --> 00:57:56.198
Why don't we...

759
00:57:56.667 --> 00:57:58.738
go live by ourselves in a remote place?

760
00:58:00.468 --> 00:58:01.807
Jae Hyun.

761
00:58:03.437 --> 00:58:05.678
All I need is you, Soo Jin.

762
00:58:07.107 --> 00:58:08.477
I don't need anyone else.

763
00:58:12.578 --> 00:58:14.718
Well, I...

764
00:58:20.787 --> 00:58:23.028
What is it? Is there something outside?

765
00:58:39.008 --> 00:58:40.747
(The last episode will be aired tomorrow.)

